OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with rain across
OL,7,FArgyll, drier elsewhere. Then the rest
OL,8,Fof the night will be cloudy with some
OL,9,Fpatchy rain, far south drier.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA cloudy day with some patchy
OL,12,Frain, this becoming confined to the
OL,13,FArgyll during the afternoon. Chance of
OL,14,Fa little brightness later towards the
OL,15,Fsouthern Ayrshire coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
