OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart on Wednesday with drizzly rain
OL,7,Facross Argyll, otherwise dry and
OL,8,Fbecoming sunny during the afternoon.
OL,9,FThursday and Friday dry and very warm
OL,10,Fwith sunshine, showers possible late
OL,11,FFriday.
